# Lint Skill

Run the **{{PROJECT_NAME}}** linter using **{{LINTER}}**.

## Usage

```sh
{{LINTER}}
```

## Common commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Check only | `{{LINTER}}` |
| Auto-fix | `{{LINTER}} --fix` |
| Specific path | `{{LINTER}} {{SRC_PATH}}` |

## Notes

- Run before every commit
- Fix all errors; warnings should be addressed when encountered
- Never disable lint rules inline without a comment explaining why
